description:
Remember Adam and Eve? Despite the knowledge God endowed them with, they disobeyed Him. They failed to make the right choice and they were afraid to face the consequences of their actions.  The wrong choice by  Adam and Eve led humanity to destruction. But, if we learn to commit every word and action to God, we will live a consistent Christian life. 

Follow God and live a life with great courage to stand up for what is true and what is right. Live with love through Christ. Set yourself free from sin and respond to God’s free gift of salvation. 

How about you? What is your life reflection? Is your life a mirror of a consistent Christian life?

Learn more with Pastor Sam Neves as he speaks on the importance of making the right choices as a leader and in our everyday health.
